metadata.name: Goodfellapes #1
metadata.description: Inspired by the award winning film “GoodFellas” , Our collection of 2,000+ “GoodFellape” NFTs are unique in their own right. A community focused project with traits & character qualities inspired from both BAYC & the film. Each GoodFellape is unique & algorithmically generated from over 60 traits. This family of wise guys is looking to grow.. and As far back as I can remember, I always wanted to be a gangster
